data.description: Cute Metairie cottage with two story addition has great curb appeal! The home has been very well maintained and has a brand new roof. Gleaming wood floors, abundant natural light and gracious archways characterize the original areas of the home. The kitchen has ample counter space, generous storage, stainless steel appliances (including a free standing double oven gas convection range), and vinyl plank flooring. The adjacent dining area and den open onto the covered patio and large fenced rear yard with a storage shed. Upstairs level has two bedrooms, a full bath and considerable closet space. All appliances, including washer and dryer remain. The convenient location is just a two-block walk from the Metairie St. Patrick's Day Parade route.
